              Older (Single Precision) NeutronStarCollisionVideos

          The larger runs are waiting in queue on the O2k array. This is
          with the SC98 default parameters. The projected wireframe grid
          is just for reference... it is 1/4 the actual simulation
          resolution.

          There is a lot of interesting stuff going on in 3D. Please note
          the depression that forms in the back of the neutron stars
          (kinda strange). The isometric top-view with a slice (the 3rd
          video) shows that everything is completely symmetric.

